Program: Last Word
Title: Angelo Dundee, Isi Metzstein, Oscar Luigi Scalfaro, Theo Angelopoulos
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01bbd8s
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 5 Feb 2012
Matthew Bannister on Angelo Dundee, the boxing trainer behind Muhammed Ali and fourteen other world champions. Isi Metzstein, the Glasgow based architect who designed some of Britain's most striking churches. Oscar Luigi Scalfaro, the Italian president who had a twenty year political battle with Silvio Berlusconi And Theo Angelopoulos the influential Greek director whose films reflected the modern history of his country. Show less